{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act14side", "eventName": "風雪過境", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BI-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "立雪求道", "storyInfo": "三大家族共同參與的聖獵即將開始。大殿之中，大長老與恩雅思緒交錯。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "恩雅，我希望你能爭取成為聖女。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "——為什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "喀蘭貿易如果想要在謝拉格更進一步，需要一個聖女，這是一個絕佳的機會。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "——為什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "當然，事情不會這麼簡單。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "另兩家人會有什麼盤算你我都很清楚。但是我相信你若是被雪水滴中，一定能夠通過考驗，成為聖女。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "恩雅，我知道你可以做到。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "——如果我不想呢？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "——如果我失敗了呢？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "所有的反駁和疑問，我一句都沒有說出口。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "因為我知道他會怎麼回答，他一定會說。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你姓希瓦艾什，恩雅。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g9_manoravenue", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，你快出來看，那是恩希歐迪斯老爺嗎？", "name": "謝拉格平民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼可能，明天就是上山聖獵的日子了，老爺這時候不準備給聖女的供奉，一早跑到領地來視察做什麼？", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......等等，這還真是恩希歐迪斯老爺！", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，最早人們進聖山是不許騎馱獸的。", "name": "謝拉格平民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤其是要去拜見聖女的人們，要從跨出自家門檻的第一步開始，雙掌合十，眼不離地，低著頭一路祈禱過去。", "name": "謝拉格平民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看老爺現在的樣子，莫不是他想效仿傳統？", "name": "謝拉格平民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，是啊。我是聽說過這種習俗，可老爺他......畢竟是老爺啊，竟然也要這麼低著頭一步一步走到聖山上面去。", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼呢，老爺也是耶拉岡德的子民啊，你難道也和佩爾羅契家的傻子一樣，覺得他忘了本？", "name": "謝拉格平民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在胡說什麼，我哪有這個意思！", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是替老爺擔心。你又不是不知道，另外兩家貪得無厭，老爺提出了把大權交給聖女，他們竟然還不太樂意。", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那兩家嫉妒老爺帶來的發展，連我們的鐵路都炸了，聽說是想把謝拉格封起來，然後兩家一起把我們給包了。", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們怎麼敢？在耶拉岡德的眼前動武，祂可是會動怒的。", "name": "謝拉格平民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們還有什麼不敢？", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天老爺這麼手無寸鐵地徒步走在街道上，明天又是三家帶兵在山中打獵，真不知道他們又能做出什麼傷天害理的事情！", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，可不要說這種不吉利的話！耶拉岡德在上，請保佑老爺一路平安！", "name": "謝拉格平民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上，請保佑老爺一路平安！", "name": "謝拉格平民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯老爺，沒想到今日還能見到如您這樣虔誠的上山參拜者！", "name": "謝拉格貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_198_blackd_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，帕萊老爺，我家主人因行大禮，必須一路虔誠祈禱，無法分心回應您。", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#8$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在下替老爺向您致以問候。", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#8$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_198_blackd_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無妨無妨，是我冒犯了。耶拉岡德在上，還請原諒我。", "name": "謝拉格貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過從圖里卡姆到聖山，路程遙遠，我等領民將恩希歐迪斯老爺的舉止看在眼裡，難免憂心。", "name": "謝拉格貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_198_blackd_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺早下定了決心，請不用為他擔憂。", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這一隊護衛也不會讓老爺出任何意外。", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_198_blackd_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好，願耶拉岡德賜福於希瓦艾什。", "name": "謝拉格貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_198_blackd_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也願耶拉岡德保佑您。", "name": "魏斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_198_blackd_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g4_boudoir", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總覺得，圍獵還沒有開始，野獸卻已經在驚慌了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您啊，只是從這窗格向外望，怎麼就知道野獸在驚慌了？", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "積雪在發出響動。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說來，明天聖獵時，您可要小心腳下。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......大長老到了。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#6$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_250_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我需要小心的麻煩事多著呢。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，你可做好了準備？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行裝與致辭，我都已準備好了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請大長老放心，我已經不是第一次參與大典了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此次大典不同於往日。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，恩希歐迪斯要來參拜耶拉岡德。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他願意在這種時候表示虔誠，是好事。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希瓦艾什前段時間還從蔓珠院請了許多神像，添置給領地裡沒有供奉神像的人。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯真的會一夜之間變得如此虔誠嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人，虔誠與否由祂注視，由祂評判，我等不能妄下斷言。", "name": "長老A"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但即使是那些不知耶拉岡德的蒙昧之人，一旦目視五彩極光，也會自然被感化，向祂禱告。", "name": "長老A"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由此來看，一夜之間變得虔信，反而是祂威能的展現。", "name": "長老A"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論恩希歐迪斯心中有什麼想法，他的行為是無可非議的。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然他所作所為是在維護信仰，聖女大人就不必有所顧慮。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#7$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格人終究要向千年的傳統低頭。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#7$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願如此。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了恩希歐迪斯，另外兩族的家主會和往常一樣上山等候。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你將作為聖女接受三族權力移交，要準備的絕不僅僅是一番得體的言辭。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖獵也好，大典也好，但凡你對待三家的態度稍有偏頗，人們立刻會將其解讀為一家得勢或失勢的信號。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白手中聖鈴之重，也考慮好了如何應對。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只差一樣，狩獵用的長弓，還請大長老允許我取用。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，你熟讀歷任聖女的手劄，應該清楚，聖女不必親自參與狩獵。這副長弓，你可是打算在聖獵開始的儀式上用？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女雖然不必親歷狩獵，但要是親自參與了，應該也不算對耶拉岡德不敬。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千年來蔓珠院的傳統一向如此，聖女大人，不可不顧身份。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人須代耶拉岡德接受三族奉上的獵物，代耶拉岡德將食物帶到大典賜予祂的子民。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是這獵物改為聖女大人親手狩獵而來，成何體統？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，眼下也不是適合您遊獵的季節。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說得對，千年來倒是從未有過三族將大權交還蔓珠院的先例。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是交權一事，本應為緩和之策，可這些日子以來，聖山下卻頻頻爆發混亂，將要交歸聖女的土地也被肆意毀壞。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像，他們當真不怕觸怒耶拉岡德。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德的子民正需要聖女大人去平息祂的怒火，向祂展現人們千年不變的虔誠之心。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許耶拉岡德需要聖女去傳達祂的怒火。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......聖殿之上，切莫妄言。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，“勤勞者必將掌權，懶惰者必將受苦”。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我雖然知道三族交權於聖女，並非要聖女掌握實權。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但聖女要維護信仰的地位，就不能只是等待著三族奉上結果，這並不是要展現他們的無能——而是我要首先做出表率。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若要維護，就不可能談什麼改變。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德的子民已經向前走了，他們向祂祈禱的東西一定與千年前不同。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祂也一定，無法做出與千年前相同的回應。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g7_thoroughfare", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sacrifice_intro", "key": "$sacrifice_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說老爺清晨從希瓦艾什家的老宅子出發，一路靠雙腳走到這裡，還沒有休息過，連一口水也沒喝上。", "name": "謝拉格平民C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸，我們給老爺送碗水去吧。", "name": "謝拉格平民C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真要遵照傳統的話，老爺這一路，確實要不吃不喝，不眠不休。", "name": "謝拉格平民D"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可......已經一天了，爸。去聖山的路程，到我們這鎮上才剛過半。", "name": "謝拉格平民C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且前面出了鎮子，天也要黑了，雪原上不知道會有什麼危險。", "name": "謝拉格平民C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，老爺來了......", "name": "謝拉格平民D"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黃昏的街道上，希瓦艾什的隊伍沉默地走來。恩希歐迪斯低垂著頭，雙掌合十，無聲地朝向遠方的聖山禱告。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到腳步聲的人們好奇地從窗戶探出頭，或者走出房門站在街道兩側。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_278_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸。", "name": "謝拉格平民C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是不能給老爺送碗水喝......我想跟著他到聖山腳下。", "name": "謝拉格平民C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺開工廠教我技術的時候，我就決定跟著他。現在老爺心誠，要去拜聖山，我更要跟著他。", "name": "謝拉格平民C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_280_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們一言不發地站起身，走下樓去，跟在希瓦艾什家護衛隊的後面，步入雪原。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}